(define/contract (min-operations nums target)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (define (required-bits x)
    (if (= x 0) 0
        (+ 1 (required-bits (bitwise-and (sub1 x) x)))))
  (letrec ((dfs (lambda (nums target ops)
                  (cond [(= target 0) ops]
                        [(or (null? nums) (< target (car nums))) +inf.0]
                        [else (min (dfs (cdr nums) target ops)
                                   (dfs (cdr nums) (- target (car nums)) (+ 1 ops)))])))
           (solve (lambda (nums target)
                    (let* ((sorted-nums (sort nums >))
                           (max-possible (apply + sorted-nums))
                           (min-ops (if (> max-possible target)
                                        (dfs sorted-nums target 0)
                                        +inf.0)))
                      (if (= min-ops +inf.0) -1 min-ops)))))
    (solve nums target)))
